{"tid":2182352,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實，呢排放得NPL多，成日係屋企對住個印印，好驚會比佢害死。","createTime":"2020-08-31T09:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T13:59:42.000Z","uid":37759,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f2ae2c7692f3d12ae5b902e61724fec9ee854098","tid":2182352,"uid":37759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:00:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的，唔放得假多真係唔知平時個印印朝早同下晏原來慣左淨係著住undie同bra係屋企做野。<br />\n宜家我放得多no pay leave，佢又成日唔記得我放假，結果就成日見到佢就咁底衫褲周屋行，仲要見到我都只係笑淫淫講句：sir，sorry，又唔記得著翻衫。跟住我屌佢老母講完都係唔撚去著翻衫！<br />\n下晏就老憑3點幾拿支雪條特登係我面前啜到雪雪聲，仲要問我：Sir！咁撚熱你要唔要拿碌黎啜下？<br />\n好撚彩佢個樣成個鼠王芬咁見到就不舉，但真係驚遲早比佢老屈，到時實家變+離婚。都係拿拿林補錢炒左佢算。但條氣緊唔順囉！"},{"pid":"1fa06f00bf51ef58b384d91325efd8f9eee337bc","tid":2182352,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ywmn2o1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYwmn2o1.png&h=741d6d8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b47594acdc37c6bcb03231a1a6ed340976368df","tid":2182352,"uid":37759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PYvMijQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPYvMijQ.jpg&h=5732e5f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不想變成甘，思覺失調刀冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ea16c942599b2c1802b63d9e0397f43ca29dba","tid":2182352,"uid":229353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:39:40.000Z","msg":"。。。"},{"pid":"2823fb07fa88c29938821669fb98425fe2de5596","tid":2182352,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:47:01.000Z","msg":"諗起成人台嗰啲賓印post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526fed7cc33c375d1ad1059a9c3b9c3c25d4f0b7","tid":2182352,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:59:42.000Z","msg":"Sir！咁撚熱你要唔要拿碌黎啜下？<br 